  <diagram id="Q5mxnjguWuWon7duKe69" name="Stealth">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1028" dy="694" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="fcno9wgf7SWZbkjeNU_S-1" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Stealth&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;68&quot;&gt;Detection of the player by enemies is influenced by several factors:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;70&quot; data-end=&quot;324&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot; data-is-only-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;70&quot; data-end=&quot;99&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;72&quot; data-end=&quot;99&quot;&gt;The enemy’s current state&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;100&quot; data-end=&quot;181&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;102&quot; data-end=&quot;181&quot;&gt;The distance between the player and the enemy (according to Dijkstra Map value)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;182&quot; data-end=&quot;278&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;184&quot; data-end=&quot;278&quot;&gt;The light source (the greater the visibility radius, the higher the chance of being noticed&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;279&quot; data-end=&quot;304&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;281&quot; data-end=&quot;304&quot;&gt;The Agility attribute&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;305&quot; data-end=&quot;324&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;307&quot; data-end=&quot;324&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;The Stealth skill&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;The size of the DM depends on player&#39;s dexterity and stealth skill.&lt;/div&gt;An angry enemy always sees the player until he out of the DM.&lt;div&gt;The chance of changing the enemy&#39;s state from the &quot;walking&quot; to &quot;aggressive&quot; depends on&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;player&#39;s dexterity and stealth skill, DM value and visibility state. The chance to notice for an enemy out of light should be [10..50] percent. If the enemy is within radius of the light the chance to notice the player is [50..90] percent.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fontSize=14;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="40" width="750" height="510" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
